skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: The Flash briefing uses the Orem Owlz schedule and news feeds. These feeds are updated weekly during the off-season and daily during the season which is June through September. The feeds provide information to fans of the Orem Owlz Baseball team.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
